50:12.922 --> 50:17.470
[SPEAKER_06]: But what you can't do is what the Prime Minister has done, which is to say... Well, you just said you'd resolve it.

50:17.450 --> 50:18.472
[SPEAKER_07]: So what would you do?

50:18.633 --> 50:19.294
[SPEAKER_06]: At the end of the day...

50:19.315 --> 50:23.445
[SPEAKER_07]: So you're not going to give them the 35% pay rise that they're asking for, so how would you resolve it?

50:23.465 --> 50:26.512
[SPEAKER_07]: Just standing there and saying, I'll resolve it, isn't an answer.

50:26.793 --> 50:27.494
[SPEAKER_07]: That's not a plan.

50:27.735 --> 50:28.998
[SPEAKER_07]: Prime Minister... How would you resolve it?

50:29.179 --> 50:32.587
[SPEAKER_07]: Prime Minister, your record is... Well, no, no, how would you resolve it?

50:32.727 --> 50:34.311
[SPEAKER_07]: You want to be Prime Minister.

50:34.291 --> 50:35.833
[SPEAKER_07]: How would you resolve the strike?

50:36.715 --> 50:37.616
[SPEAKER_07]: How would you resolve them?

50:37.636 --> 50:40.060
