56:14.583 --> 56:20.332
[SPEAKER_07]: I don't agree with it, because I think people who work hard and aspire to provide that education for their kids should have that freedom.

56:20.493 --> 56:22.376
[SPEAKER_07]: That's what my parents did, and I'll support it.

56:22.396 --> 56:22.877
[SPEAKER_07]: But you heard it.

56:23.197 --> 56:25.581
[SPEAKER_07]: Keir Starmer is going to raise taxes.

56:25.561 --> 56:30.192
