56:40.176 --> 56:40.958
[SPEAKER_06]: Well, I do need to answer that.

56:40.978 --> 56:42.642
[SPEAKER_06]: That's not the start, and that's not the end.

56:42.622 --> 56:44.825
[SPEAKER_06]: I do need to answer that, because he put that figure out there.

56:44.845 --> 56:45.346
[SPEAKER_06]: Very briefly.

56:45.366 --> 56:48.009
